[{"ave_id":"AVE-2009-0017","file_name":"2009/AVE-2009-0017.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2009-5114","title":"WebGlimpse wgarcmin.cgi 目录遍历漏洞","description":"WebGlimpse 2.18.7 及更早版本中的 wgarcmin.cgi 脚本存在目录遍历漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向 DOC 参数传递包含 `..`（点点）序列的特制请求，利用路径回溯技术突破目录限制，读取服务器上任意文件，包括敏感配置文件、密码文件等。该漏洞无需身份认证即可利用，攻击复杂度低，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2009-5114"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2012-03-19T18:55:02.327","updated":"2026-06-16T23:15:06.623","remediation":"升级 WebGlimpse 至 2.19.0 或更高版本，该版本已修复 wgarcmin.cgi 中 DOC 参数的目录遍历漏洞。若厂商已停止维护，建议迁移至其他活跃维护的搜索工具（如 Apache Solr、Elasticsearch），并在 Web 服务器层配置输入过滤规则，拦截包含 `../` 等路径遍历特征的请求。同时确保 wgarcmin.cgi 脚本对 DOC 参数做路径规范化检查，拒绝非授权路径访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://websecurity.com.ua/2628/","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/74321","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/36994","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2009/CVE-2009-5114.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2009/CVE-2009-5114.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/1482f62c613998b0fe0690591034b732c0bb2e0a/http/cves/2009/CVE-2009-5114.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/de9949dedbd4d7d071222d7c816d86aa68e1eb86/cves/2009/5xxx/CVE-2009-5114.json","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd29577590f076c89dec5c30d809d68f210/5001-to-6000-templates/cve-2009-5114-1483.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2009-5114.js","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2009-5114_38.yaml","https://github.com/CriticalMatterial/NucleiTemplates/blob/2c4c9867bfbda69385d06f819577cbb7b35758e1/cves/2009/CVE-2009-5114.yaml","https://github.com/amad3us47/amad3us47.github.io/blob/07cfc0edf465277028554b47198f6f186d3215b6/data/cve-2009-5114-1481.yaml","https://github.com/w4n95/vuls-data-raw-exploit-inthewild/blob/2c8c2568a21a9cc77244882f65c37bca47d71613/2009/CVE-2009-5114.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/f2d12f176efdb99f18928b2678d34b7fa4f530f8/content/CVE-2009-5114.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2009/AVE-2009-0017.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2009-0016","file_name":"2009/AVE-2009-0016.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2009-5020","title":"AWStats awredir.pl 开放重定向漏洞","description":"AWStats 6.95 之前版本中的 awredir.pl 脚本存在开放重定向漏洞（CWE-20：输入验证不当）。远程攻击者可通过特制请求，利用该漏洞将用户重定向至任意恶意网站，进而实施钓鱼攻击窃取敏感信息。攻击者无需身份认证即可发起攻击，但需诱使用户点击恶意链接，CVSS 评分 5.8，危害等级中。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.8,"aliases":["CVE-2009-5020"],"sources":["cve","nuclei"],"published":"2010-12-02","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级 AWStats 至 6.95 或更高版本以修复 awredir.pl 中的开放重定向漏洞。如无法升级，在 Web 服务器层面对 awredir.pl 脚本的访问添加 URL 白名单校验规则，限制重定向目标仅为受信任域名。同时检查 Web 日志中是否存在利用该漏洞的异常重定向请求。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://awstats.sourceforge.net/docs/awstats_changelog.txt","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2009/CVE-2009-5020.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2009/CVE-2009-5020.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/de9949dedbd4d7d071222d7c816d86aa68e1eb86/cves/2009/5xxx/CVE-2009-5020.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/f29605a96fd1261602d83e1b34d001cc853a7340/nvdcve/CVE-2009-5020.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2009/AVE-2009-0016.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2009-0015","file_name":"2009/AVE-2009-0015.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2009-4679","title":"Joomla! iF Portfolio Nexus 目录遍历漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 iF Portfolio Nexus (com_if_nexus) 组件 1.5 版本存在目录遍历漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向 index.php 传递包含 `..` 序列的 controller 参数触发该漏洞，实现任意本地文件的包含与执行，可能导致敏感信息泄露或远程代码执行。该漏洞影响 Joomla! 中使用该组件的网站，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2009-4679"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-03-08T15:30:00.480","updated":"2026-06-16T23:14:09.170","remediation":"立即卸载或禁用 Joomla! 的 com_if_nexus 组件（版本 1.5），此组件已停止维护且不再有官方补丁。作为临时缓解，可修改 index.php 对 controller 参数进行严格过滤，拒绝包含 `..` 的路径字符串，或删除该组件目录彻底消除风险。建议迁移至其他仍在维护的 Joomla! 图库组件替代 iF Portfolio Nexus。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://secunia.com/advisories/37760","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/10754","http://www.osvdb.org/61382","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/37473","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/33440","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2009/CVE-2009-4679.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2009/CVE-2009-4679.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/1482f62c613998b0fe0690591034b732c0bb2e0a/http/cves/2009/CVE-2009-4679.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/de9949dedbd4d7d071222d7c816d86aa68e1eb86/cves/2009/4xxx/CVE-2009-4679.json","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd29577590f076c89dec5c30d809d68f210/5001-to-6000-templates/cve-2009-4679-1476.yaml","https://github.com/ARPSyndicate/suricata-vedas/blob/fe24794ad36564b5bbc7c69101525011387b8650/2009/CVE-2009-4679.rules","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2009-4679_31.yaml","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/32d2bf74aba181d7e166ecf9becdff3983874bd2/CVE-2009/CVE-2009-46xx/CVE-2009-4679.json","https://github.com/ahisec/Lots-of-POC/blob/51ed84ccc21e97e5e12563150992e03f9de384cd/nuclei/inertialfate/com_if_nexus/CVE-2009-4679.yaml","https://github.com/rix4uni/nucleihub-templates/blob/579a0234551b9e0e322460a62dc77bd6109e4aff/nucleihub-templates/CVE-2009-4679-1472.yaml","https://github.com/lianqingsec/NucleiPocGather/blob/dcce204f62196117b9c95c52d8101ccf7a5d27bc/poc/cve/cve-2009-4679-1472.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2009/AVE-2009-0015.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2009-0014","file_name":"2009/AVE-2009-0014.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2009-4223","title":"Gianni Tommasi KR-Web 远程文件包含漏洞","description":"KR-Web 内容管理系统（又称 Kr-php Web Content Server）1.1b2 及更早版本中的 adm/krgourl.php 文件存在 PHP 远程文件包含漏洞。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向 DOCUMENT_ROOT 参数传递包含恶意 PHP 代码的外部 URL，导致任意代码执行，进而完全控制目标服务器。该漏洞利用难度低且影响范围较广，危害严重。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2009-4223"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2009-12-07T17:30:00.500","updated":"2026-06-16T23:13:16.477","remediation":"立即停止使用 KR-Web 1.1b2 及更早版本，该产品已长期无人维护，官方未发布安全补丁。彻底卸载 kr-php Web Content Server，改用其他受支持的内容管理系统（如 WordPress、Joomla）。若因业务原因无法替换，在 php.ini 中将 allow_url_include 设为 Off 并重启 Web 服务，同时用 Web 应用防火墙（WAF）拦截包含 DOCUMENT_ROOT 参数的异常请求。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/10216","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/54395","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/10216","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2009/CVE-2009-4223.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2009/CVE-2009-4223.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/1482f62c613998b0fe0690591034b732c0bb2e0a/http/cves/2009/CVE-2009-4223.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/de9949dedbd4d7d071222d7c816d86aa68e1eb86/cves/2009/4xxx/CVE-2009-4223.json","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/high/cve-2009-4223-1465.yaml","https://github.com/lianqingsec/NucleiPocGather/blob/dcce204f62196117b9c95c52d8101ccf7a5d27bc/poc/cve/CVE-2009-4223_53.yaml","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd29577590f076c89dec5c30d809d68f210/5001-to-6000-templates/cve-2009-4223-1468.yaml","https://github.com/linuxadi/40k-nuclei-templates/blob/542be6820c801c02a33aee60f1c05ca7b0b5005f/aditya/folder2/CVE-2009-4223_%E9%87%8D%E5%A4%8D%E5%89%AF%E6%9C%AC.yaml","https://github.com/gongzeq/VAPT3/blob/3576a7accf5cbadc8e64924d6ff48393db379ea7/secbot/resource/poc/cve/cve-2009-4223-1465.yaml","https://github.com/rix4uni/nucleihub-templates/blob/579a0234551b9e0e322460a62dc77bd6109e4aff/nucleihub-templates/CVE-2009-4223-1467.yaml","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2009-4223_45.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2009/AVE-2009-0014.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2009-0013","file_name":"2009/AVE-2009-0013.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2009-4202","title":"Joomla Omilen Photo Gallery 组件 0.5b 本地文件包含漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 Omilen Photo Gallery 组件（com_omphotogallery）Beta 0.5 版本存在目录遍历漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向 index.php 的 controller 参数传递包含目录遍历序列（如 ../）的特制请求，实现包含并执行服务器上的任意本地文件。该漏洞源于程序对用户输入的 controller 参数缺乏充分的路径过滤与安全检查，攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，可能导致敏感信息泄露或进一步代码执行。CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级为高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2009-4202"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2009-12-04T19:30:00.547","updated":"2026-06-16T23:13:14.093","remediation":"立即卸载 Joomla! 的 Omilen Photo Gallery Beta 0.5 组件，该组件已停止维护且无修复版本。可在 Joomla! 后台扩展管理器中将其卸载，并替换为其他仍在维护的相册组件（如 Phoca Gallery 或 JoomGallery）。若暂时无法卸载，需在 Web 服务器层面（如 Apache .htaccess）添加规则，过滤 controller 参数中的目录遍历序列（如 ../ 和 %2e%2e/），阻止恶意请求访问 /index.php?option=com_omphotogallery。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/8870","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/35201","http://www.vupen.com/english/advisories/2009/1494","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/8870","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2009/CVE-2009-4202.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2009/CVE-2009-4202.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/5e5a4a501f58d16b9c64206b909c369249097140/http/cves/2009/CVE-2009-4202.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/de9949dedbd4d7d071222d7c816d86aa68e1eb86/cves/2009/4xxx/CVE-2009-4202.json","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/high/cve-2009-4202-1459.yaml","https://github.com/exploit-io/nuclei-templates/blob/a4b7182985a6e45df346cfe45242d40455e152b5/templates/cve-2009-4202-1462.yaml","https://github.com/linuxadi/40k-nuclei-templates/blob/542be6820c801c02a33aee60f1c05ca7b0b5005f/aditya/folder2/cve-2009-4202-1461.yaml","https://github.com/hack007x/veil_poc/blob/5cfe1da6e975ba816d728597885a5c5e79bda8bd/cves/2009/CVE-2009-4202.poc","https://github.com/cckuailong/reapoc/blob/699762e4c31d0183733f64313d8fc3be6470bd37/2009/CVE-2009-4202/poc/nuclei/CVE-2009-4202.yaml","https://github.com/coreruleset/seaweed-reports/blob/3e2a1bd3dbca1b431f18ed0dabb71fa729d4d059/2022/Nov/06/lfiArtifact/lfiReport.csv","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2009-4202_32.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2009/AVE-2009-0013.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2009-0012","file_name":"2009/AVE-2009-0012.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2009-3318","title":"Joomla! com_album 组件 1.14 目录遍历漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 Roland Breedveld Album (com_album) 组件 1.14 版本中存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向 index.php 传递含有 `../` 序列的恶意 target 参数，绕过路径限制访问服务器上的任意目录，可能导致敏感信息泄露或其他未明确的安全影响。该漏洞无需身份认证即可远程利用，影响所有运行该组件的 Joomla! 站点。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2009-3318"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2009-09-23T12:08:35.360","updated":"2026-06-16T23:11:22.553","remediation":"建议立即卸载 Roland Breedveld 开发的 com_album 1.14 组件，该组件自 2007 年后未再更新，厂商已停止维护，不再存在安全补丁，应彻底移除以免继续受目录遍历攻击威胁。如暂时无法卸载，可在 Web 服务器层面（Apache/Nginx）配置规则拒绝 `target` 参数含有 `../` 的请求，或在 WAF（如 mod_security）中添加 `SecRule ARGS:target \"\\.\\.\" \"deny\"` 规则作为临时缓解，同时尽快迁移至其他受支持的 Joomla! 相册扩展。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/9706","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/36441","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/9706","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2009/CVE-2009-3318.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2009/CVE-2009-3318.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/490586283f9ca1596471e5230c91d74f96495bb9/http/cves/2009/CVE-2009-3318.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/de9949dedbd4d7d071222d7c816d86aa68e1eb86/cves/2009/3xxx/CVE-2009-3318.json","https://github.com/cckuailong/reapoc/blob/699762e4c31d0183733f64313d8fc3be6470bd37/2009/README.md","https://github.com/ARPSyndicate/suricata-vedas/blob/fe24794ad36564b5bbc7c69101525011387b8650/2009/CVE-2009-3318.rules","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2009-3318_51.yaml","https://github.com/CyberSecAI/cve_dedup/blob/35ff6751d9dde6c89382c34106bf8165b6ade361/data_out/CVE_similarity/CVE/CVE-2010-1878.json","https://github.com/felipetruman/NucleiFuckWorld/blob/cf7f22d5d1832b6e55e44e812857734b250a1004/fuckBounty-templates/http/cves/2009/CVE-2009-3318.yaml","https://github.com/ibnufachrizal/dotfiles-public/blob/68073686f2b3153143ac0c00b39d39387c3eff78/.config/nuclei/resume-cbhb0bobqofijmlm0mog.cfg","https://github.com/lianqingsec/NucleiPocGather/blob/dcce204f62196117b9c95c52d8101ccf7a5d27bc/poc/cve/cve-2009-3318-1456.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2009/AVE-2009-0012.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2009-0011","file_name":"2009/AVE-2009-0011.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2009-3053","title":"Joomla Agora 组件 3.0.0b 本地文件包含漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 Agora 组件 3.0.0b 版存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过 index.php 访问 avatars 页面，在 action 参数中注入目录遍历序列（如 ../），从而包含并执行服务器上的任意本地文件，可能导致敏感信息泄露或远程代码执行。CVSS 评分 6.8，危害等级中等，影响使用该组件的 Joomla! 网站。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.8,"aliases":["CVE-2009-3053"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2009-09-03T17:30:10.187","updated":"2026-06-16T23:10:48.597","remediation":"升级 Agora 组件至 3.0.0c 及以上版本（若厂商已停止维护则直接卸载 com_agora 组件）；临时缓解措施可在 Web 应用防火墙（WAF）层面对 index.php 中 action 参数添加目录遍历序列（如 ../）的过滤规则，或在 Joomla! 后台禁用该扩展模块。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/9564","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/36207","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/52964","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/9564","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2009/CVE-2009-3053.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2009/CVE-2009-3053.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/490586283f9ca1596471e5230c91d74f96495bb9/http/cves/2009/CVE-2009-3053.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/de9949dedbd4d7d071222d7c816d86aa68e1eb86/cves/2009/3xxx/CVE-2009-3053.json","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/high/cve-2009-3053-1451.yaml","https://github.com/lianqingsec/NucleiPocGather/blob/dcce204f62196117b9c95c52d8101ccf7a5d27bc/poc/cve/cve-2009-3053-1449.yaml","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2009-3053_20.yaml","https://github.com/rix4uni/nucleihub-templates/blob/579a0234551b9e0e322460a62dc77bd6109e4aff/nucleihub-templates/CVE-2009-3053_1.yaml","https://github.com/lianqingsec/NucleiPocGather/blob/dcce204f62196117b9c95c52d8101ccf7a5d27bc/poc/cve/cve-2009-3053