置中限制 URL 参数并部署 WAF 规则过滤目录遍历序列，防止读取 /etc/passwd、配置文件等任意本地文件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://osvdb.org/55176","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/35378","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/8946","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2009/CVE-2009-2100.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2009/CVE-2009-2100.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/490586283f9ca1596471e5230c91d74f96495bb9/http/cves/2009/CVE-2009-2100.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/de9949dedbd4d7d071222d7c816d86aa68e1eb86/cves/2009/2xxx/CVE-2009-2100.json","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd29577590f076c89dec5c30d809d68f210/5001-to-6000-templates/cve-2009-2100-1446.yaml","https://github.com/youki992/VscanPlus/blob/714a0e276a538a22c1a6215c71458a8b59a920ef/pocs_yml/nucleiFiles/http/cves/2009/CVE-2009-2100.yaml","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v2/C/CVE-2009-2100_1.yaml","https://github.com/itsmenaga/Nuclei-Templates-All/blob/7e93c24e44969db15f4072e1c6a322a026452d6b/Vulnerability-Templates/cve-2009-2100-1445.yaml","https://github.com/elijah-bennett0/IntentLimit/blob/bcfe225cf61ee454aa53896f7f3120246f52119f/tools/exploitation/CrazyIngrate/exploits/cve_2009_2100/config.yaml","https://github.com/rishikesh-j/Nuclei-Templates-Scrapped/blob/c1c4a009b3ada12b7923dcbc40e099ce8f224b2c/templates/cve-2009-2100-1442.yaml","https://github.com/coreruleset/seaweed-reports/blob/3e2a1bd3dbca1b431f18ed0dabb71fa729d4d059/2022/Nov/27/Artifact/Report.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2009/AVE-2009-0010.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2009-0009","file_name":"2009/AVE-2009-0009.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2009-2015","title":"Joomla! MooFAQ 组件本地文件包含漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 MooFAQ 组件（com_moofaq）1.0 版本中的 includes/file_includer.php 存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向 file 参数传递包含 `../` 序列的恶意路径读取服务器上的任意文件，导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞无需身份认证即可远程利用，影响范围包括使用该组件的所有 Joomla! 网站。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2009-2015"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2009-06-09T19:30:00.250","updated":"2026-06-16T23:08:34.823","remediation":"该第三方组件 MooFAQ (com_moofaq) 1.0 已停止维护，官方未发布安全补丁。建议立即在 Joomla 后台卸载该组件；若必须使用，可手动修改 components/com_moofaq/includes/file_includer.php，在接收 file 参数后添加 realpath() 路径规范化检查和 basename() 过滤，禁止包含 ../ 等目录跳转序列，并设置 open_basedir 限制 PHP 文件访问范围。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://secunia.com/advisories/35370","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/35259","http://www.vupen.com/english/advisories/2009/1530","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/8898","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2009/CVE-2009-2015.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2009/CVE-2009-2015.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/490586283f9ca1596471e5230c91d74f96495bb9/http/cves/2009/CVE-2009-2015.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/de9949dedbd4d7d071222d7c816d86aa68e1eb86/cves/2009/2xxx/CVE-2009-2015.json","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/high/cve-2009-2015-1439.yaml","https://github.com/linuxadi/40k-nuclei-templates/blob/542be6820c801c02a33aee60f1c05ca7b0b5005f/aditya/folder4/cve-2009-2015-1440.yaml","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/e23d633136851fc6026957a1a4f6f4626b866fab/CVE/data/2009/CVE-2009-2015.json","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v2/C/cve-2009-2015.yaml","https://github.com/ARPSyndicate/suricata-vedas/blob/fe24794ad36564b5bbc7c69101525011387b8650/2009/CVE-2009-2015.rules","https://github.com/0xelixer/new/blob/6f6dd4a43a76ce74c1e8cc0558629a2ea198286e/nuclei-temps/cent/template1/cve-2009-2015-1438.yaml","https://github.com/coreruleset/seaweed-reports/blob/3e2a1bd3dbca1b431f18ed0dabb71fa729d4d059/2023/Feb/12/Reports/lfiReport.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2009/AVE-2009-0009.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2009-0007","file_name":"2009/AVE-2009-0007.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2009-1558","title":"Linksys WVC54GCA 无线摄像头目录遍历漏洞","description":"Cisco Linksys WVC54GCA 无线视频监控摄像头 firmware 1.00R22 及 1.00R24 版本的 adm/file.cgi 脚本存在目录遍历漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证，通过在 next_file 参数中传入编码的 %2e%（即编码后的 \"..\"）或绝对路径，即可突破路径限制读取设备上的任意敏感文件（如配置文件、密码等）。攻击复杂度低，无需用户交互，可能导致设备敏感信息泄露，进而被利用进行更深层次的攻击。受影响的设备包括 Linksys WVC54GCA 系列无线摄像头。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.8,"aliases":["CVE-2009-1558"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2009-05-06T16:30:00.627","updated":"2026-06-16T23:07:31.290","remediation":"该设备已停产且官方未发布修复此目录遍历漏洞的补丁。建议升级至最终固件 1.1.00 build 2（可能修复部分安全问题），并将摄像头隔离在独立 VLAN 中，通过防火墙限制只有特定内网 IP 能访问 TCP 80/443 端口，同时禁止在路由器上为该设备做端口转发；如需远程访问，应通过 VPN 接入内网后再管理。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.gnucitizen.org/blog/hacking-linksys-ip-cameras-pt-3/","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/34713","http://www.vupen.com/english/advisories/2009/1173","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/50231","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/32954","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2009/CVE-2009-1558.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2009/CVE-2009-1558.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/490586283f9ca1596471e5230c91d74f96495bb9/http/cves/2009/CVE-2009-1558.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/de9949dedbd4d7d071222d7c816d86aa68e1eb86/cves/2009/1xxx/CVE-2009-1558.json","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/high/cve-2009-1558-1428.yaml","https://github.com/exploit-io/nuclei-templates/blob/a4b7182985a6e45df346cfe45242d40455e152b5/templates/cve-2009-1558-1426.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2009-1558.js","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v2/C/CVE-2009-1558-1426_1.yaml","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd29577590f076c89dec5c30d809d68f210/5001-to-6000-templates/cve-2009-1558-1425.yaml","https://github.com/u21h2/nacs/blob/1eaa239ded7496317a47073605c8ddda70686ef5/web/poc/pocs_dev/nucleibak/cves/2009/CVE-2009-1558.yaml","https://github.com/rix4uni/nucleihub-templates/blob/579a0234551b9e0e322460a62dc77bd6109e4aff/nucleihub-templates/CVE-2009-1558-1425.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2009/AVE-2009-0007.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2009-0006","file_name":"2009/AVE-2009-0006.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2009-1496","title":"Joomla! Cmi Marketplace 目录遍历漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 Cmi Marketplace 组件（com_cmimarketplace）0.1 版本中存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者通过向 index.php 传递含有 `..`（点点）序列的 viewit 参数，可遍历服务器上任意目录，泄露敏感文件路径信息。该漏洞无需身份认证即可远程利用，危害等级中危。目前官方尚未发布补丁，建议禁用该组件或限制 viewit 参数输入。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2009-1496"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2009-05-01T16:30:00.233","updated":"2026-06-16T23:07:23.623","remediation":"立即在 Joomla 后台卸载 com_cmimarketplace 组件（扩展管理→管理→查找并卸载）。若无法卸载，在网站根目录 .htaccess 中添加 RewriteRule ^index\\.php.*viewit=.*\\.\\..* - [F,L] 拦截目录遍历请求；同时限制 index.php?option=com_cmimarketplace 仅允许可信管理 IP 访问。该组件已停止维护，建议迁移至仍在更新的替代组件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/34431","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/8367","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2009/CVE-2009-1496.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2009/CVE-2009-1496.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/490586283f9ca1596471e5230c91d74f96495bb9/http/cves/2009/CVE-2009-1496.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/de9949dedbd4d7d071222d7c816d86aa68e1eb86/cves/2009/1xxx/CVE-2009-1496.json","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd29577590f076c89dec5c30d809d68f210/5001-to-6000-templates/cve-2009-1496-1421.yaml","https://github.com/khulnasoft-bot/OSVIC/blob/a4eeee61d1cb6e295191ee863ea67fbf018e3353/CVE/data/2009/CVE-2009-1496.json","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2009-1496_26.yaml","https://github.com/1in9e/gosint/blob/bdda4461515c4398c08638676bbbfe451b73ff95/client/vuln_scan/nuclei/tools/nuclei-templates/cves/2009/CVE-2009-1496.yaml","https://github.com/lianqingsec/NucleiPocGather/blob/dcce204f62196117b9c95c52d8101ccf7a5d27bc/poc/cve/cve-2009-1496-1421_1.yaml","https://github.com/coreruleset/seaweed-reports/blob/3e2a1bd3dbca1b431f18ed0dabb71fa729d4d059/2023/Mar/05/Reports/lfiReport.csv","https://github.com/merlinepedra25/SCA4ALL/blob/aa2e7f5a64567d2f7b12e4c4ac171229e5b081eb/config/nuclei-templates/cves/2009/CVE-2009-1496.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2009/AVE-2009-0006.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2009-0005","file_name":"2009/AVE-2009-0005.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2009-1151","title":"phpMyAdmin 配置文件静态代码注入漏洞","description":"phpMyAdmin 的 /config/config.inc.php 配置文件中存在静态代码注入漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过 setup.php 页面的 save 操作向配置文件写入任意 PHP 代码，进而获得远程代码执行权限。该漏洞影响 phpMyAdmin 2.11.x 系列早于 2.11.9.5 版本及 3.x 系列早于 3.1.3.1 版本，CVSS 评分 9.8，危害等级严重。由于无需认证即可利用且存在公开的 Metasploit 利用模块，实际攻击风险极高。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.8,"aliases":["CVE-2009-1151"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2009-03-26","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"立即升级 phpMyAdmin 至 2.11.9.5 或 3.1.3.1 及以上版本；删除或限制访问 /setup/ 目录，在 Web 服务器配置中添加访问控制规则禁止外部访问 setup.php；禁用 config 目录的写入权限；如无法升级，可临时移除 config/config.inc.php 文件并设置 $cfg['SetupDisable'] = true。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.phpmyadmin.net/home_page/security/PMASA-2009-3.php","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/8921","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/16913","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/34236","http://www.debian.org/security/2009/dsa-1824","http://security.gentoo.org/glsa/glsa-200906-03.xml","http://lists.opensuse.org/opensuse-security-announce/2009-04/msg00003.html","http://secunia.com/advisories/34430","http://secunia.com/advisories/34642","http://secunia.com/advisories/35585","http://secunia.com/advisories/35635","http://www.mandriva.com/security/advisories?name=MDVSA-2009:115","http://www.gnucitizen.org/blog/cve-2009-1151-phpmyadmin-remote-code-execution-proof-of-concept/","http://labs.neohapsis.com/2009/04/06/about-cve-2009-1151/","https://www.cisa.gov/known-exploited-vulnerabilities-catalog?field_cve=CVE-2009-1151"],"poc_urls":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/8921"],"exp_urls":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/16913"],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2009/AVE-2009-0005.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2009-0004","file_name":"2009/AVE-2009-0004.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2009-0932","title":"Horde Horde_Image 驱动参数本地文件包含漏洞","description":"Horde 及 Horde Groupware 的 framework/Image/Image.php 中存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向 Horde_Image::factory 方法的 driver 参数传入包含目录遍历序列（如 ../）的特制字符串，绕过访问限制实现任意本地文件的包含与执行。该漏洞影响 Horde 3.2.4 以下及 3.3.3 以下版本、Horde Groupware 1.1.5 以下版本，CVSS 评分 6.4，危害等级中危。厂商已发布升级版本修复此漏洞，建议用户及时更新。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-2009-0932"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2009-03-17T21:30:00.313","updated":"2026-06-16T23:06:08.290","remediation":"升级 Horde Framework 至 3.2.4 及以上版本（或 3.3.3 及以上版本），升级 Horde Groupware 至 1.1.5 及以上版